== English ==

=== Etymology ===

By analogy with [[nerf bar]].  Invented by ATV racer Brian Fry in 1985.

=== Noun ===

# A net running between a [[nerf bar]] on a vehicle and the vehicle itself, in order to prevent the driver's leg getting caught between the two.
#: ''Those nerf nets may look weird, but they've saved me a lot of pain.''